<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谷仓的门被人从外面紧紧地锁住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们听到了农夫詹金斯的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谷仓里可能来了郊狼。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许有人想偷咱们的马。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>詹金斯的儿子回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿上枪，以防万一。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33547</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫詹金斯叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“枪？”赛伊倒吸了一口冷气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得想想办法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们四处看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有地方可以让他们藏起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这个时候，农夫詹金斯离谷仓越来越近了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很怕。”简哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟朝着梯子跑过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有主意了。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们爬回到二楼去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他人在想她要干什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>詹金斯和他的儿子已经站在了门外。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是钥匙，爸。”儿子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抖了抖钥匙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我猜我们没有其他选择了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊悄声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跟在潘瑟后面爬回了二层。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比和简迅速地跟上了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“帮我把这个拉上来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟命令说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟和赛伊把梯子拉了上去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把梯子拖到了打开的窗户那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在明白了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>年纪大一点儿的孩子们将梯子从窗户伸了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们将梯子靠在了谷仓的外墙上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129345</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快来，简！”赛伊叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从梯子上爬下去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134890</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要是掉下去怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用力吸了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不会掉下去的，我会拉着你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向她保证说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简爬了出去，顺着梯子下去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，潘瑟跟着她下去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一楼，农夫詹金斯和他儿子正在开最后一把锁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不管谁在里面，我都听到你的声音了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫詹金斯大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172341</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你逃不了了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>轮到鲍比了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他迅速跟上了她的姐妹们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，谷仓大门朝两侧飞快地打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大门发出了一声巨响。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊可以听到农夫詹金斯和他儿子在楼下的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你在这儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫詹金斯用生气的声音说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“赛伊！赛伊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的兄弟姐妹们在谷仓外压低声音拼命地叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊做了一个深呼吸，然后爬了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们头都没回地以最快速度跑走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回家后，玛莎阿姨生气了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看看现在外面天黑成什么样了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她斥责道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们很抱歉。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我太生气了。上楼回房间去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨抱起了兰姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍巴？赛伊？嘻嘻！嘻嘻！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰姆开心地大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他张开了双臂，仿佛那是他的翅膀，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后摆出了要飞的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许兰姆真的看到我们了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们看看彼此笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“最后我们还是没有挨饿啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊拍了拍自己的肚子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>互相说了晚安后，孩子们回到了自己的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，玛莎阿姨给孩子们做了烤薄饼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我要去见朋友。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们必须照顾小宝宝。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296933</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把兰姆抱给了潘瑟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会在晚餐的时候回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，巴斯家的孩子们带着兰姆一起去见休伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多可爱的小人儿啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他充满热情地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰姆指着休伊说：“猪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他说什么，猪？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊的笑容消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是，他，嗯，他说的是大。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>86</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊紧张地笑着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>87</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦， 轮到潘瑟许愿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>88</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他的妹妹摇摇头说：“我不想许愿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>89</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>340999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>345176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么不呢？”其他孩子问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>90</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>345177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>351288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“每次许愿之后总是会发生一些糟糕的事情。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>91</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>351289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得我们不应该再来见休伊了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>92</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>355566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>360703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，我有个愿望。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>93</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>360704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>364009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你说吧。”休伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>94</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>364010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>369324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望我们可以见到恐龙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>